msgstr "居中(&R)"

#: kdm-appear.cpp:157
msgid "Spec&ify"
msgstr "指定(&I)"

#: kdm-appear.cpp:169
msgid ""
"You can choose whether the login dialog should be centered or placed at "
"specified coordinates."
msgstr "您可以选择登录对话框是居中放置或在指定的坐标放置。"

#: kdm-appear.cpp:178
