msgstr "在这里您指定登录对话框的<em>中心</em>的座标。"

#: kdm-appear.cpp:204
msgid "GUI S&tyle:"
msgstr "GUI 风格(&T)："

#: kdm-appear.cpp:212
msgid "You can choose a basic GUI style here that will be used by KDM only."
msgstr "您可以选择仅被 KDM 使用的基本的图形用户界面风格。"

